      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability, practicality, and the opportunity to put their own finishing touches on it. A sensible choice for commuting, a first car, or a backup vehicle.",
