    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of character? This car is a budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy runaround. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s got honest value, a solid presence on the road, and a lot of potential for the right buyer. If you\u2019re realistic and want something inexpensive that could still be put to good use, this could be a great fit. Priced to attract interest and open to a fair conversation.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong runner with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels solid enough for a dependable budget driver, work car, or weekend project. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the hard parts make this one worth a look for someone who appreciates a straightforward, mechanical platform with practical upside. Priced to move and easy to justify for the right buyer.",
      "price": 5900.0,
